# Force LF for text files on every platform so Windows checkouts
# don't trigger prettier CRLF mismatch on Sanity (windows-latest).
# Pre-this-file behaviour: git's `core.autocrlf=true` default on
# Windows converted LF → CRLF on checkout, prettier saw mixed line
# endings, and `format:check` failed for every text file. Setting
# `text eol=lf` here is the single source of truth that overrides
# the per-user autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Lockfile is line-noise — never diff or merge it manually.
bun.lock -diff -merge

# Binary assets — let Git treat them as opaque.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
